	mesh = {Humans; Hippocampus; Alzheimer Disease; Male; Female; Magnetic Resonance Imaging; TDP-43 Proteinopathies; Aged; Atrophy; Positron-Emission Tomography; Aged, 80 and over; Cognitive Dysfunction; Cross-Sectional Studies; tau Proteins; Dementia},
